# WrappingExponentiable - Protocol for types that support wrapping exponentiation (**%)
module Core

### Defines the protocol `WrappingExponentiable`.
protocol WrappingExponentiable
  ### Implements the wired routine behavior for this value.
  ### :param you: The other value to compare against.
  ### :returns: The resulting `Me` value.
  @readonly
  routine Me.$pow_wrap(you: Me) -> Me
